ygData.messageBody:
You go on vacation for a week and wow, this list went crazy.. had like 160
eqbard emails. So forgive me but i deleted a lot of them. If anything
REALLY important happened and you're bored, send me a note and give the the
condensed scoop :)

On the positive side, played my bard for the first time in a LONG time, it
was a blast :)
Got level 28 and played in Dalnir, first time in a dungeon really :) I was
scardededed.

Anyway, hope you're all well!

Halana, 56th Shaman
Tani, 28th Bardette
Paradigm
Solusek Ro
